    <h2>Welcome to Our Mammal Exhibit</h2>
    <p>Welcome to our mammal exhibit, where you'll encounter the fascinating world of mammals! Immerse yourself in the diversity and wonder of these captivating creatures, each with its own unique characteristics and behaviors.</p>
    <p>Embark on a journey through our carefully curated exhibits, where you'll discover the majesty of lions, the grace of giraffes, and the playfulness of monkeys. From the stealthy predators to the gentle herbivores, every mammal offers a glimpse into the rich tapestry of life on Earth.</p>
    <p>Whether you're drawn to the powerful roar of big cats or the adorable antics of primates, our mammal exhibit offers something for everyone. Join us in celebrating the extraordinary diversity of mammals and exploring their habitats, right here in our sanctuary of wonder and awe.</p>
